<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/the-anatomy-of-trumpocracy-an-interview-with-noam-chomsky/">The Anatomy of Trumpocracy: An Interview With Noam Chomsky</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The current Trumpocracy thrives on the demolition of unions and the neoliberal atomization of society.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/c-j-polychroniou/" itemprop="url" rel="author">C.J. Polychroniou</a></span>, </dd>
