<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/politics-and-elections/' rel='section' class='politics-and-elections' style='color: #1958aa;'>Politics &amp; Elections</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-on-fascism-showmanship-and-democrats-hypocrisy-in-the-trump-era/">Noam Chomsky on Fascism, Showmanship and Democrats&#8217; Hypocrisy in the Trump Era</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Amid the hypocritical posturing of both parties, Trump&#8217;s severe assault on the common good continues.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/c-j-polychroniou/" itemprop="url" rel="author">C.J. Polychroniou</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://truthout.org' itemprop='url'>Truthout</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2018-06-20T13:40:16+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2018-06-20T13:40:16+00:00">June 20, 2018</time>
