<h3 class="hellobar-title"><span class="show-for-medium" style="color:#c42b35">$35,000 to raise — we need your help!
</span>
<span class="show-for-small-only" style="color:#c42b35">$35,000 to raise — we need your help!
</span></h3>
<div class="row">
<p class="hellobar-description"><span class="show-for-medium">When it comes to waging war, stripping basic rights, election fraud, or a global health crisis, there is no such thing as "alternative facts." Choose media that's been exposing government and corporate exploitation since day one: <b>Donate now to help us raise the $35,000 we need to keep publishing fearless journalism.</b></span>
<span class="show-for-small-only">When it comes to war, election fraud, or a global health crisis, there's no such thing as "alternative facts." Choose media that's been exposing government &amp; corporate exploitation since day one: <b>Donate now to help us keep publishing.</b>
</span></p>
